divs: Sighting DetailsWe were on vacation. I was excited about the mountains we were coming up to. Ihad never seen mountains. We were not paying much attention to theaircrafts.There were several jet planes flying around on what we thought wereprobubly training flights. I was taking pictures of the scenery not the ufo. Ididnt realize I had till I had the film developed. It was an accident. Myhusband had a photographer friend of his check out the picture. He couldntexplain it. It may be nothing but I would like to have it checked out.
